Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.77,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}名为乐器的红线
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.23,0:23:31.08,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将我们紧密相连
